    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you say that, but it's not just in my head. i see them sighing when they walk into my room, or how they look at each other when they think i'm not watching. it's like they're just doing their duty. it would be so much easier for them if they didn't have to worry about my appointments and my meds and all this... it feels selfish to keep making them do it.",
