      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a terrible burden to carry, and the pain you feel is real. However, the idea that your absence would bring them freedom is a cruel illusion that ignores the deep, unspoken love they hold for you. Stepping aside would not free them; it would leave them with a void they cannot fill, and you would be left alone with the guilt of having taken away their only source of comfort. Please consider that your continued presence, however difficult, is the very thing that holds their world together.",
